{
  "id": "adv_main_03_12_02",
  "title": "BIG4編1章57話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私、アイドルってなんなのか\n自分なりの答えが、やっと見つけられました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I…\n…finally found my own answer to what an idol is‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9698791152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.9131525356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9131525356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……今まで、沢山考えてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ve thought about it a lot‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3788438081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.4614969492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "初めは、ただお姉ちゃんの後を追いかけて\nこの世界に入りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I just followed in my sister’s footsteps\nand entered this world‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、さくらにお姉ちゃんの歌を託して\nお姉ちゃんにも、もう後は追いかけないって伝えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I entrusted my sister’s song to Sakura-chan‚\nand told my sister that I wouldn’t chase after her anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3333331585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 35.1670301994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私は『長瀬麻奈の妹』じゃなくて\n『長瀬琴乃』として道を歩もうと思えたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to think about walking my own path‚\nnot as “Mana Nagase’s little sister”‚ but as “Kotono Nagase”‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.8144906919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃のことか……\n琴乃もさくらも、決断には勇気が必要だっただろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That time‚ huh…\nBoth Kotono and Sakura-chan‚ you needed courage to make that decision‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの五人でまっすぐ突き進んで、サニピとも……\nさくらとも並んで歩いて行けると思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we could move forward together with the five of us in Moon Tempest‚\nand walk side-by-side with Sunny Peace…with Sakura-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5333331585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 62.138730836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "だけど……私達はスリクスに勝てなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…we couldn’t beat IIIX‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.138730836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.3720641852
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.092200033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "そしてサニピは自分達の答えを見つけて\nスリクスに勝って、BIG4になった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Sunny Peace found their own answer‚\nbeat IIIX‚ and became a BIG4 group‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333331585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてなんだろう、って思いました\n同じように頑張ってきたのに……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wondered why‚\nEven though we’ve worked hard in the same way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.4440793117
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、月ストもサニピも\n練習やライブにずっと全力で取り組んでいたからな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that both Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace\n…have always been giving their all to practice and lives…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9333331585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 91.3403607131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "だけど……だからこそ、これ以上どうしたらいいか\n分からなくなったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…because of that‚\nI didn’t know what to do anymore‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 101.8663266581
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 101.8663266581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "頑張って、頑張って、頑張って走って、それでも選んだ\n道は行き止まりで、何度選び直しても行き止まりで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after working hard‚ and hard‚ and running hard‚ the path I chose\n…was a dead end‚ and no matter how many times I tried to choose again‚ it was a dead end‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 117.4361677887
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "そんな中でどりきゅんと戦って、負けて……\nああ、本当にもう、前に進めないのかなって思いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the midst of that‚ I fought DoriKyun‚ and lost…\n…and I thought‚ ah‚ I really can’t move forward anymore‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "心に雲がかかって、他の道さえ見えなくなって……\nそれでもなんとか前に進みたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Clouds covered my heart‚ and I couldn’t even see other paths…\nBut I still wanted to move forward somehow‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 143.9875275692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "だから……みんなとの絆を無理やり断ち切ってでも\n暗闇へ走り出したんです。その先に何かがあると信じて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so…even if it meant forcibly severing my ties with everyone…\n…I started running into the darkness‚ Believing that there was something ahead‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.0999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 158.3916086596
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 160.7333331585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "月ストを脱退したのは自分勝手だったと思います\n沢山の人に迷惑をかけて、渚達を泣かせてしまったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it was selfish of me to leave Moon Tempest‚\nI caused trouble for a lot of people‚ and made Nagisa cry‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.2999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の脱退の決断が最善だったとは思わない\nけれど……その気持ちまで否定することは出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think your decision to leave was the best one‚ Kotono‚\nbut…I can’t deny your feelings‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.9999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 178.9291148585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9291148585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 180.9161050957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、「今こうして琴乃が戻って来たんだから\n結果オーライ」だなんて気楽に言うつもりはないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I’m not going to say something carefree\nlike‚ “It’s all okay because Kotono came back”‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.033339262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だけどあの時……琴乃が一人で走る決断をして\n渚達は四人で走る決断をした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at that time…Kotono decided to run alone‚\nand Nagisa decided to run with the four of them‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃も、渚も、沙季も、すずも、芽衣も……\n五人それぞれが、暗闇の中を進んできた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ Nagisa‚ Saki‚ Suzu‚ Mei…\n…all five of you walked through the darkness‚",
